<hw>Ab*bre"vi*ate</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An abridgment.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Elyot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Abbreviated</ent>⟦br⟧
